<welcome :user="user" inline-template>
    <div class="main-content">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1">
                    <div class="panel panel-dark">
                        <div class="panel-body centered">
                            <h2><strong>BlackMailApp</strong> will help you get what you always wanted...</h2>
                            <h1 class="big-monies">Money!</h1>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-4">
                    <div class="panel panel-dark">
                        <div class="panel-body centered">
                            <h3>In 3 Easy Steps:</h3>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="panel panel-dark">
                        <div class="panel-body centered">
                            <h1 class="in-a-circle">1</h1>
                            <p>Find a suitable target. Someone who you've got some tasty blackmail material on.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="panel panel-dark">
                        <div class="panel-body centered">
                            <h1 class="in-a-circle">2</h1>
                            <p>Use our app to send them a notification (anonymously!) that they can pay up or it will be released to an information channel of your choosing.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="panel panel-dark">
                        <div class="panel-body centered">
                            <h1 class="in-a-circle">3</h1>
                            <p>Enjoy the results. Either take the money that they pay or send out that delicious blackmail you're holding. Either way, you win.*</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <br/>
                <br/>
                <br/>
                <br/>
                <br/>
                <br/>
                <br/>
                <br/>
                <br/>
                <br/>
                <br/>
                <br/>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="full-width">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row disclaimer">
                    <div class="col-sm-12">
                        <p class="pull-left">* Rasputin Labs also wins. Always.</p>
                        <p class="pull-right">&copy; 2017 Rasputin Labs</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</welcome>
